Package com.iplanet.ums

Interface IUMSConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssignableDynamicGroup, BaseRole, COSTemplate, DirectCOSDefinition, DomainComponent, DynamicGroup, EntityManager, FilteredRole, ManagedRole, Organization, OrganizationalUnit, PeopleContainer, PersistentObject, Resource, SchemaManager, StaticGroup, User
    public interface IUMSConstants
    This interface represents a collection of common constants used by the classes in UMS. Classes implementing this interface can use these constants. The constants pertain to messages defined in properties files.
